title: Static Analysis

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows applications to change network connectivity state.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.PERSISTENT_ACTIVITY.description: Allows an application to make parts of itself persistent, so that the system can't use it for other applications.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.READ_LOGS.description: Allows an application to read from the system's various log files. This allows it to discover general information about what you are doing with the phone, potentially including personal or private information.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.READ_SMS.description: Allows application to read SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. Malicious applications may read your confidential messages.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS.description: Allows application to receive and process SMS messages. Malicious applications may monitor your messages or delete them without showing them to you.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.WRITE_CALENDAR.info: add or modify calendar events and send emails to guests
android.permission.WRITE_CALENDAR.description: Allows an application to add or change the events on your calendar, which may send emails to guests. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your calendar events or to send emails to guests.

android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to modify the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your contact data.

android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

android.permission.WRITE_SMS.description: Allows application to write to SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. Malicious applications may delete your messages.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to external storage.

android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to read the sync settings, such as whether sync is enabled for Contacts.

android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to modify the sync settings, such as whether sync is enabled for Contacts.

android.permission.READ_USER_DICTIONARY.description: Allows an application to read any private words, names and phrases that the user may have stored in the user dictionary.

android.permission.WRITE_USER_DICTIONARY.description: Allows an application to write new words into the user dictionary.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows access to the list of accounts in the Accounts Service.

android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to perform operations like adding and removing accounts and deleting their password.

android.permission.CLEAR_APP_CACHE.description: Allows an application to free phone storage by deleting files in application cache directory. Access is usually very restricted to system process.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.

android.permission.KILL_BACKGROUND_PROCE.description: Allows an application to kill background processes of other applications, even if memory is not low.

android.permission.FLASHLIGHT.description: Allows the application to control the flashlight.

android.permission.WRITE_SECURE_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to modify the system's secure settings data. Not for use by common applications.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD.description: Allows applications to disable the keyguard if it is not secure.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from external storage.

android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG.description: Allows an application to read the user's call log.

android.permission.WRITE_CALL_LOG.description: Allows an application to write (but not read) the user's call log data.

android.permission.BIND_ACCESSIBILITY_SE.description: Must be required by an AccessibilityService, to ensure that only the system can bind to it.

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.lookout.ui.LoadDispatchActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. The deterministic RBG is seeded by an entropy source that accumulates entropy from a platform-based DRBG and a software-based noise source, with a minimum of 256 bits of entropy at least equal to the greatest security strength (according to NIST SP 800-57) of the keys and hashes that it will generate.

"about_text" : "スマートフォン向けセキュリティ企業であるLookoutは、すべてのスマートフォンユーザーに安全なモバイル環境を提供することに注力しています。 Lookoutの詳細情報については、https://www.lookout.com/jpをご覧ください。 セキュリティ Lookoutはモバイル環境のマルウェアやスパイウェアなどの脅威からデバイスを自動的に保護します。 個人情報検出機能(プレミアム) Lookoutは位置情報、個人情報、アドレス帳、メッセージなどの個人データにアクセス可能なアプリを特定します。 セーフブラウジング(プレミアム) Lookoutはフィッシング詐欺、マルウェア、悪意のあるサイトからスマートフォンを保護し、安心して Webを閲覧できる安全な環境を提供します。 バックアップ Lookoutはアドレス帳データを安全な方法で Web上に保存します。保存されたデータは https://www.lookout.com/jpからダウンロードまたは復元できます。Lookoutプレミアムでは画像や通話履歴のバックアップも可能です。 端末捜索 Lookoutでは紛失したデバイスを地図上で検索し、大音量の警報を起動することができます。この機能を有効にするには、Webブラウザでhttps://www.lookout.com/jpにアクセスします。Lookoutプレミアムではデバイスをリモートでロックし、データをワイプすることもできます。 サポートとフィードバック ご質問や問題点については、support-jp@lookout.comまでお問い合わせください。 製品に関するアイデアやフィードバックについては、feedback@lookout.comまでお問い合わせください。 Lookoutでは社員も募集しております。詳細については、https://www.lookout.com/about/careersをご覧ください。 Lookoutプレミアム Lookoutはすべてのユーザーに無料で提供されているサービスです。Lookout有料版も提供されています。Lookoutプレミアムにアップグレードすることで、個人情報検出機能、セーフブラウジング、リモートロック、リモートワイプ、画像と通話履歴のバックアップ、新しいデバイスへのデータ転送、プレミアムサポートなどの追加セキュリティおよびプライバシー保護機能をご利用いただけます。月間および年間サブスクリプションプランもご用意しております。"

"about_text" : "El objetivo de nuestra compañía es lograr que el uso de dispositivos móviles sea más seguro para todo el mundo. Puedes obtener más información sobre Lookout en https://www.lookout.com/es Seguridad Lookout protege automáticamente tu dispositivo móvil contra malware, spyware y otras amenazas. Analizador de apps (Premium) Lookout identifica las apps que pueden tener acceso a tus datos confidenciales, por ejemplo, a tu ubicación, información de identidad, contactos y mensajes. Navegación segura (Premium) Lookout te permite navegar de forma segura por Internet desde tu móvil, sin preocuparte del phishing, el malware o de sitios malintencionados. Backup Lookout almacena de modo seguro tus contactos en Internet. Puedes descargar o restaurar tus datos desde https://www.lookout.com/es. Con Lookout Premium puedes hacer copias de seguridad de tus fotos y del historial de llamadas. Dispositivo perdido Lookout puede localizar en un mapa tu dispositivo perdido y activar una fuerte alarma. Para usar estas funciones, entra en https://www.lookout.com/es desde cualquier navegador. Con Lookout Premium también puedes bloquear tu dispositivo y borrar tus datos de forma remota. Soporte y comentarios Ponte en contacto con ayuda@lookout.com si tienes preguntas o problemas o si quieres dejar algún comentario. Tenemos algunos puestos por cubrir. Únete a nuestro equipo. https://www.lookout.com/about/careers Lookout Premium Lookout es un servicio gratuito disponible para todos los usuarios. También existe una versión de pago de Lookout. Cambia a Lookout Premium para obtener una mayor seguridad y protección de tus datos confidenciales con funciones como el Analizador de apps, la Navegación segura, Bloquear y borrar en remoto, el Backup de fotos e historial de llamadas, la transferencia de datos a un nuevo dispositivo y el soporte Premium. Disponemos de planes de suscripción mensuales y anuales."

"about_text" : "Somos uma empresa de segurança para smartphones dedicada a tornar a experiência móvel segura para todos. Saiba mais sobre nossa empresa visitando o nosso site: https://www.lookout.com/br Segurança O Lookout protege você automaticamente de malware, spyware e outras ameaças. Analisador de apps (Premium) O Lookout identifica apps que podem acessar seus dados privados, incluindo sua localização, informações de identidade, contatos e mensagens. Navegação segura (Premium) O Lookout permite que você navegue com segurança na Internet em seu telefone sem se preocupar com golpes, malware ou sites maliciosos. Backup O Lookout armazena de maneira segura os seus contatos na Internet. Você pode possível baixar ou restaurar seus dados pelo site https://www.lookout.com/br. Com o Lookout Premium, também é possível fazer o backup de imagens e do histórico de chamadas. Dispositivo perdido O Lookout pode encontrar seu dispositivo perdido e fazer soar bem alto quando você quiser. Acesse https://www.lookout.com/br em qualquer navegador para utilizar estes recursos. Com o Lookout Premium, também é possível bloquear ou apagar seus dados de maneira remota. Suporte e feedback Entre em contato através do e-mail ajuda@lookout.com caso tenha dúvidas ou problemas. Tem comentários, idéias ou sugestões sobre o produto? Escreva para feedback@lookout.com e compartilhe com a gente. Estamos contratando! Junte-se à nossa equipe. https://www.lookout.com/about/careers Lookout Premium O Lookout é um serviço gratuito disponibilizado para todos os nossos usuários. Há também uma versão paga disponível – o Lookout Premium. Faça o upgrade para a versão Premium para ter maior segurança e proteção de privacidade, incluindo os recursos Analisador de Apps, Bloqueio Remoto, Limpeza Remota, Backup de Fotos e Histórico de Chamadas, transferência de dados para um novo dispositivo e Suporte Premium. Temos planos mensais e anuais."

"about_text" : "Nous sommes une société spécialisée dans la sécurisation de l'utilisation des portables au quotidien. Pour en savoir plus sur notre société, consultez https://www.lookout.com/fr Sécurité Lookout protège automatiquement votre portable contre les logiciels malveillants, espions et autres. Info confidentialité (Premium) Lookout identifie les applications capables d'accéder à vos données privées, y compris votre emplacement, vos identifiants, vos contacts et vos messages. Navigation sûre (Premium) Lookout vous permet de surfer sur le web en toute sécurité depuis votre portable sans vous préoccuper de l'hameçonnage, des logiciels malveillants ou des intrusions. Sauvegarde Lookout sauvegarde vos contacts sur le web. Vous pouvez télécharger ou restaurer vos données à partir de https://www.lookout.com/fr. Avec Lookout Premium, vous pouvez aussi sauvegarder vos images et votre historique d'appels. Portable égaré En cas de perte, Lookout peut localiser votre portable sur une carte et activer une alarme. Accédez à https://www.lookout.com/fr depuis n'importe quel navigateur web pour utiliser ces fonctions. Avec Lookout Premium, vous pouvez aussi verrouiller votre portable et en effacer les données à distance. Assistance et commentaires Contactez aide@lookout.com pour toute question ou problème éventuel. Nous recrutons ! Rejoignez notre équipe. https://www.lookout.com/about/careers Lookout Premium Lookout est un service gratuit à la disposition de tous les utilisateurs. Une version payante de Lookout est également disponible. Souscrivez à Lookout Premium pour une meilleure protection de vos données, y compris des fonctions d'analyse d'applications, navigation sûre, verrouillage à distance, effacement à distance, sauvegarde de vos photos et historique d'appels, transfert des données vers un nouveau portable, et assistance Premium. Des programmes de souscription mensuels et annuels sont disponibles."

"about_text" : "Naša tvrtka je pružatelj rješenja za zaštitu pametnih telefona koja su osmišljena kako bi svima omogućili sigurnije korištenje mobilnih uređaja. Saznajte više o našoj tvrtki na adresi https://www.lookout.com Sigurnost Aplikacija Lookout automatski vas štiti od zlonamjernih i špijunskih programa te ostalih prijetnji na mobilnim uređajima. Čuvar privatnosti (Premium) Aplikacija Lookout otkriva aplikacije koje mogu pristupiti vašim privatnim podacima, uključujući vašu lokaciju, identifikacijske podatke, kontakte i poruke. Sigurno pretraživanje (Premium) Aplikacija Lookout omogućava vam sigurno pretraživanje interneta na vašem telefonu, a da pritom ne trebate brinuti o krađi identiteta, zlonamjernim programima ili štetnim stranicama. Backup Aplikacija Lookout pohranjuje vaše kontakte na sigurno mrežno mjesto. Preuzmite ili dohvatite svoje podatke na stranici https://www.lookout.com. Ako ste korisnik verzije Premium aplikacije Lookout, možete također izraditi backup fotografija ili povijesti poziva. Izgubljen uređaj Aplikacija Lookout može utvrditi položaj vašeg izgubljenog uređaja na karti i uključiti reprodukciju alarma. Posjetite adresu https://www.lookout.com u bilo kojem od mrežnih preglednika kako biste koristili ove značajke. Ako koristite verziju Premium aplikacije Lookout, također možete udaljeno zaključati svoj uređaj i izbrisati podatke s njega. Podrška i povratne informacije Ako imate bilo kakvo pitanje, problem ili ako želite poslati povratnu informaciju, pošaljite elektroničku poruku na support@lookout.com. Zapošljavamo! Postanite članom ekipe. https://www.lookout.com/about/careers Verzija Premium aplikacije Lookout Aplikacija Lookout je besplatna i dostupna svim korisnicima. Također je dostupna i verzija aplikacije Lookout koja se plaća. Nadogradite na verziju Premium aplikacije Lookout kako biste koristili dodatne značajke za zaštitu sigurnosti privatnosti poput čuvara privatnosti, sigurnog pretraživanja, udaljenog zaključavanja, udaljenog brisanja, izrade backupa fotografija i povijesti poziva, prijenosa podataka na novi uređaj i izvrsne korisničke podrške. Možete odabrati između mjesečnih i godišnjih pretplatničkih paketa."

"about_text" : "Задача нашей компании - обеспечить защиту мобильных устройств и смартфонов, а также сделать работу на них безопасной. Подробную информацию о компании можно найти на вебсайте https://www.lookout.com/ru Безопасность Lookout автоматически защищает мобильные устройства от вредоносного и шпионского ПО, а также от других угроз безопасности. Защита данных (Premium) Lookout способен определить, какие из приложений имеют доступ к вашей личной информации, такой как контакты и сообщения, идентификационные данные и данные о местоположении. Интернет-защита (Premium) Установив Lookout, вы сможете безопасно открывать веб-страницы на мобильном устройстве, не волнуясь из-за таких вещей, как фишинг, вредоносное ПО или веб-сайты злоумышленников. Резервное копирование Lookout хранит ваш список контактов на надежном сервере в Сети. Вы можете загрузить или восстановить свои данные с веб-сайта https://www.lookout.com/ru. Lookout Premium, кроме того, позволяет создавать резервные копии изображений и журнала вызовов. Пропавшее устройство Lookout может показать местоположение потерянного устройства на карте и включить на нем сирену. Эти функции доступны из любого веб-браузера на сайте https://www.lookout.com/ru. Lookout Premium позволяет также дистанционно заблокировать устройство и стереть данные на нем. Поддержка и обратная связь С любым вопросом и любой проблемой можно обратиться по адресу support-ru@lookout.com. Мы набираем сотрудников! Присоединяйтесь к нашей команде. https://www.lookout.com/about/careers Lookout Premium Lookout - бесплатный для всех пользователей сервис. Но часть услуг предоставляется за плату. Lookout Premium включает ряд дополнительных сервисов обеспечения безопасности: Защита данных, Интернет-защита, Дистанционная блокировка, Резервное копирование фотографий и журнала вызовов, Перенос данных на новое устройство и доступ к премиум-поддержке. Оплата производится помесячно или раз в год."

"about_text" : "Sicher und smart mit Lookout! Wir sorgen für Sicherheit im mobilen Leben. App-Berater (Premium) Lookout identifiziert Apps, die Zugriff auf Ihre persönlichen Daten haben, darunter Ihren Standort, Informationen zu Ihrer Identität, Kontakte und Nachrichten. Sicher Surfen (Premium) Lookout ermöglicht Ihnen das sichere Surfen im Internet über Ihr Mobilgerät, ohne dass Sie sich um Phishing, Malware oder bösartige Websites sorgen müssen. Backup Lookout speichert Ihre Kontakte sicher im Internet. Sie können Ihre Daten von https://www.lookout.com/de herunterladen und wiederherstellen. Mit Lookout Premium können Sie auch Bilder und Ihre Anrufliste speichern. Geräteortung Lookout kann Ihr verlorenes Gerät auf einer Karte orten und eine laute Sirene auslösen. Gehen Sie von jedem beliebigen Webbrowser aus auf https://www.lookout.com/de, um diese Funktionen zu nutzen. Mit Lookout Premium können Sie Ihr Gerät auch aus der Ferne sperren und Ihre Daten löschen. Support & Feedback Kontaktieren Sie bitte hilfe@lookout.com bei Fragen oder Problemen. Wir freuen uns auch über Feedback! Wir stellen ein! Bereichern Sie unser Team! https://www.lookout.com/about/careers Lookout Premium Lookout ist ein kostenloser Service für alle Benutzer. Es gibt auch eine bezahlte Version, die mehr Funktionen und erweiterte Features umfasst. Holen Sie sich Ihr Upgrade zu Lookout Premium für zusätzliche Sicherheit und Privatsphären-Schutz, darunter Lookouts App-Berater, Sicher Surfen, Fernsperren, Fernlöschen, Backup von Fotos und Anrufliste, Datenübertragung auf ein neues Gerät und Premium-Support. Es stehen monatliche und jährliche Abonnements zur Auswahl."

playstore_details.title: Mobile Security, Antivirus & Cleaner by Lookout
playstore_details.description:
Mobile Security & Antivirus by Lookout provides premium mobile security & identity protection for all of your Android devices.

Secure your device and your life, with Lookout. Lookout provides instant security from viruses, threats and personal data theft. 

Lookout is the only all-in-one mobile security & antivirus app that protects your mobile device, your data & your identity. Stay ahead of any virus with our antivirus features, phishing attacks or other mobile theft breach with the Mobile Security & Antivirus app by Lookout.

Lookout Basic Includes:
► FREE Mobile Security & Antivirus
► App Scanning: Continuous, over-the-air antivirus protection from viruses, malware, adware, & phishing
► System Advisor: Checks your mobile device for root detections to make sure the operating system is working properly
► Lookout makes it easy to identify, clean & remove viruses from your Android device.
► Locate & Alert: Map the location of your device & make it sound an alarm - even on silent!
